{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_2000-06-10-3",
 "title": "A Close Finish at the Arena",
 "summary": "In the stands of the Reckless Abandon Swoop Arena, the disguised agent Bazil McKenzie (as Mege Vauki) watches another grueling race alongside the diplomat Eva Sargent, the old soldier Halloway, and the injured Colonel Altair Quila. While the announcer calls a tight contest dominated by Simone in the Terminal Velocity and the absent McTavish, Halloway and Quila fall into shop talk about military life and her swift rise to colonel after the post-Endor disbandments. Sargent listens quietly, keeping an eye on Captain Howie Darklighter's run aboard the Firedancer, while Bazil drifts to a screen to watch the carnage as a Wampa savages the racer Tarrin. The race ends in a near photo finish, with Howie clawing up to a proud second place and the various pilots limping or being carried across the line.",
